Welcome to the DLB documentation!
===================================

DLB is a collection of tools targeting HPC applications. 
Its main goal is to help with the dynamic load balancing of hybrid codes, which use a nested parallelism model e.g MPI + OpenMP.
DLB provides components to **modify ressources at runtime**, as well as a profiler to **gather performance metrics**. 

.. note::
   If you are new here, consider having a look at the :ref:`overview` first.


If you want to contribute, please have a look at our `GitHub repository <https://github.com/bsc-pm/dlb/>`_.


